{"schemaVersion":1,"bookId":"toefl-sentences","unitId":"sentence-005","title":"Sentence 05","sectionId":"sentences-001","sectionTitle":"Sentence 01-10","pageStart":42,"pageEnd":48,"extractionMethod":"text-layer","wordEntryCount":35,"duplicateEntryCount":0,"pages":[{"number":42,"blocks":[{"type":"title","text":"Sentence 05"},{"type":"text","text":"The greater the population there is in a locality, the greater the need"},{"type":"text","text":"there is for water, transportation, and disposal of refuse."},{"type":"text","text":"一个地方的人口越多，其对水、交通和垃圾处理的需求就会越"},{"type":"text","text":"大。"},{"type":"section","text":"语法笔记"},{"type":"text","text":"这是一个“the more ..., the more”的句型，表示“越…，就越…”，是"},{"type":"text","text":"一个复合句。"},{"type":"section","text":"核心词表"},{"type":"entry","text":"population /ˌpɑːpjuˈleɪʃn/ n. （统称）某领域的生物；族群；人口","headword":"population"},{"type":"note","text":"记忆 popul（人）+ation（表名词）→人口"},{"type":"note","text":"搭配 population distribution 人口分布"},{"type":"note","text":"同根 populate v. （大批地）居住于"},{"type":"entry","text":"locality /loʊˈkæləti/ n. 地点；位置","headword":"locality"},{"type":"note","text":"记忆 local（地方）+ity→地点；位置"},{"type":"note","text":"同义 position n. 位置"},{"type":"note","text":"同根 location n. 位置，场所"},{"type":"entry","text":"transportation /ˌtrænspɔːrˈteɪʃn/ n. 运输；运输系统","headword":"transportation"},{"type":"note","text":"记忆 trans（转移）＋port（运）+ation→从一个地方拿到另一个地"},{"type":"text","text":"方→运输"}]},{"number":43,"blocks":[{"type":"note","text":"搭配 public transportation 公共交通"},{"type":"text","text":"transportation system 运输系统"},{"type":"text","text":"transportation network 交通网络"},{"type":"note","text":"同义 transit n. 运输"},{"type":"note","text":"同根 transport n./vt. 运输"},{"type":"entry","text":"disposal /dɪˈspoʊzl/ n. 清除；处理","headword":"disposal"},{"type":"note","text":"搭配 garbage disposal 垃圾处理"},{"type":"text","text":"at one’s disposal 任由某人处理"},{"type":"note","text":"同义 get rid of 处理，丢掉"},{"type":"note","text":"同根 dispose v. 处理，处置"},{"type":"entry","text":"refuse /ˈrefjuːs/ n. 废物；垃圾","headword":"refuse"},{"type":"text","text":"/rɪˈfjuːz/ v. 拒绝"},{"type":"note","text":"搭配 refuse collection 垃圾收集"},{"type":"note","text":"同义 garbage n. 垃圾"},{"type":"text","text":"rubbish n. 垃圾"},{"type":"text","text":"litter n. 垃圾"},{"type":"section","text":"主题归纳"},{"type":"text","text":"航空交通工具："},{"type":"entry","text":"aircraft /ˈerpleɪn/ n. 飞机","headword":"aircraft"},{"type":"note","text":"搭配 aircraft maintenance飞机维修"},{"type":"entry","text":"airliner /ˈerlaɪnər/ n. 大型客机；班机","headword":"airliner"},{"type":"text","text":"civil aviation 民用航空"},{"type":"text","text":"commercial jet 商业喷气机"},{"type":"entry","text":"helicopter /ˈhelɪkɑːptər/ n. 直升飞机","headword":"helicopter"}]},{"number":44,"blocks":[{"type":"text","text":"水运交通工具："},{"type":"text","text":"cruise ship游艇"},{"type":"entry","text":"ferryboat /ˈfɛrɪbəʊt/ n. 渡船，渡轮","headword":"ferryboat"},{"type":"note","text":"记忆 ferry（摆渡）+boat（船）→渡船"},{"type":"entry","text":"rowboat /ˈroʊboʊt/ n. 划艇","headword":"rowboat"},{"type":"note","text":"记忆 row（划船）+boat（船）→划艇"},{"type":"entry","text":"vessel /ˈvesl/ n. 大船；轮船","headword":"vessel"}]},{"number":45,"blocks":[{"type":"note","text":"搭配 ocean-going vessel远洋轮船"},{"type":"entry","text":"yacht /jɑːt/ n. 快艇，游艇","headword":"yacht"},{"type":"text","text":"路运交通工具："},{"type":"entry","text":"automobile /ˈɔːtəməbiːl/ n. 汽车","headword":"automobile"},{"type":"note","text":"记忆 auto（自动）+mobile（可移动的）→汽车"},{"type":"entry","text":"automotive /ˌɔːtəˈmoʊtɪv/ a. 汽车的，机动车辆的","headword":"automotive"},{"type":"entry","text":"bicycle /ˈbaɪsɪkl/ n. 自行车；脚踏车","headword":"bicycle"},{"type":"note","text":"搭配 electric bicycle电动自行车"},{"type":"entry","text":"caravan /ˈkærəvæn/ n. 旅行拖车，大篷车","headword":"caravan"},{"type":"text","text":"electric tram 电车"},{"type":"text","text":"hybrid car 混合动力车"},{"type":"entry","text":"lorry /ˈlɔːri/ n. 货运汽车","headword":"lorry"},{"type":"note","text":"搭配 lorry crane 货车吊机"},{"type":"entry","text":"motor /ˈmoʊtər/ n. 汽车","headword":"motor"},{"type":"entry","text